# Test 8: Functions
Set global_result to 0.

Create a function called greet_alice:
    Show "Hello, Alice!".
End function.

Create a function called greet_bob:
    Show "Hello, Bob!".
End function.

# Test function calls
Call greet_alice.
Call greet_bob.

# Function that sets a global
Create a function called set_global:
    Set global_result to 42.
End function.

Call set_global.
Show "Global result: " plus global_result.
